    {
      "id": "role-content-node",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Content-Bearing Nodes",
      "position": {
        "x": 820,
        "y": 140
      },
      "width": 360,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Content-Bearing Nodes\n\n**Role:** content is optional composition, not universal nodehood.\n\nExamples:\n- `markdown`\n- graph-local content classes\n- document or tutorial cards\n\nThese carry the subject matter of the graph when the graph needs content.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
